{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/StoreSubject_Introduce.gif?t=1725942268\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/Store_CastleEntrance.png?t=1725942268\" /><br><br>The world has come to an end.<br>All civilizations disappeared, and the empty places seem to be occupied by the monsters.<br><br>Led by their last lingering feelings of the extinct world, the few survivors each happen to gather in a castle built on a fief.  <br><br>They were born into different races, have lived in different places, and have different purposes.<br>Now they have to work together to achieve their own specific goals.<br><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/StoreSubject_FourProtagonist.gif?t=1725942268\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/Store_Protagonist.png?t=1725942268\" /><br><br>Each character has different stories and different skill sets.<br>Some parry off or avoid enemy attacks, but some fight recklessly, ignoring their damage.<br><br>Face your reckless enemies with every four characters with a different style of play.<br><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/StoreSubject_Tools.gif?t=1725942268\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/Store_SkillChange.png?t=1725942268\" /><br><br>You can choose and use each character's skills.<br>Each skill can be strengthened in different ways through Glyphs and increase performance when you level up with each character. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/_SHANA_GameplayRecord_012.gif?t=1725942268\" /><br><br>And can overcome the moment of crisis with scrolls and strengthen yourself through relics.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/StoreSubject_Hideout.gif?t=1725942268\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/Store_Hideout.png?t=1725942268\" /><br><br>If you lose a battle, you lose progress and return to your hideout, but that doesn't mean a complete reset.<br><br>You can unlock permanent reinforcement in hiding places, discover new artifacts, or find ways to speed up your next exploration.<br><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/StoreSubject_Exploration.gif?t=1725942268\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/Store_WorldMap.png?t=1725942268\" /><br><br>The environment and enemies encountered in each expedition may vary, but the castle structure is fixed.<br>You may also be able to find a new path in the castle.<br><br>And you will have to choose your move of direction every time you encounter the next node.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/StoreSubject_Features.gif?t=1725942268\" /><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A skill-based roguelike (rogue-lite) action game with 4 main characters.<br></li><li> Cinematic videos where each character's story exists.<br></li><li> Powerful bosses, randomly combined champions, dozens of monsters.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hideout","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1935100/a988d180ae0d96ef3491af40afe2a27df0715e20.jpg"},{"name":"Fury","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1935100/de